00:55.770 --> 00:57.490
[They were tied to the other side,
not the top.]

00:57.580 --> 01:01.360
As if they wanted you to get lost.

01:01.860 --> 01:03.540
What about the yellow ribbon?

01:03.670 --> 01:04.670
[Anything on this?]

01:04.760 --> 01:07.740
Why are you asking
about yellow the ribbon?

01:07.910 --> 01:11.270
Was there anything else?
Like, did you see someone suspicious?

01:11.520 --> 01:13.539
No, I don't think so.

01:15.010 --> 01:18.030
[Someone murdered my colleague.]

01:19.710 --> 01:21.730
Who gave you the yogurt drink?

01:22.780 --> 01:26.640
[The hiker looking at the pink rucksack
handed him a yogurt.]

01:26.810 --> 01:29.330
Since then, he felt dizzy and nauseous

01:30.000 --> 01:31.930
and even hallucinated.

01:36.090 --> 01:37.600
[And that person is]

01:37.690 --> 01:39.370
[still on this mountain.]

01:41.340 --> 01:42.850
[Killing people]

01:42.979 --> 01:44.530
[on this mountain]

01:44.870 --> 01:46.289
